\pard\sa80\cf1\fs20\lang1033 Tauntauns are a species of omnivorous reptomammals who are indigenous to the icy planet of Hoth. Tauntauns were commonly used as pack animals by Hoth's denizens.\par
Tauntauns are also used as patrol mounts since they are so well-adapted to the cold.\par
